-- ds.page: add-plan
id: add-plan-api

-- ds.markdown:

This API collects all the plan details from the user and adds it as a record in the [Plan](id: plan-schema) model

URL: `<service-endpoint>/api/add-plan/`

Request Type: `POST`

For every plan, it needs the following parameters:
- instance_name
- vcpus
- ram
- plan_name
- description
- charge_per_min